<h3>Setting local or remote configuration</h3>

<ul class="noleft">
<li><a href="#remote">Setting remote configuration</a></li>

<li><a href="#local">Setting local configuration</a></li>
</ul>

<table border="1" bordercolor="navy" bgcolor="#FFFFE1" cellpadding="10%">
<tr>
<td class="noteme" bordercolor="#ffffe1"><b>Note</b> <br>
All the Configuration Manager functionalities can be accessed from <span class="UI_COMMAND" id="MenuBar_Document_Tools.msg+MenuBar_Document_Tools+1667">Tools</span><img src="../../images/general/litarr2.gif"><span class="UI_COMMAND" id="MenuBar_Empty_Tools.msg+MenuBar_Empty_Tools+7276">Configuration Manager</span><img src="../../images/general/litarr2.gif">..., when no document is open.</td>
